"If re-drawing is required because a variable or something else changed, "
"call :ref:`CanvasItem.queue_redraw <class_CanvasItem_method_queue_redraw>` "
"in that same node and a new ``_draw()`` call will happen."
msgstr ""
"Si es necesario redibujar porque una variable o alguna otra cosa ha "
"cambiado, llama :ref::ref:`CanvasItem.queue_redraw "
"<class_CanvasItem_method_queue_redraw>` en el nodo y se llamará de nuevo a "
"``_draw()``."

